====== H7716: שֶׂה ======

===== Source =====

or   ; probably from  H7582  through the idea of   out to graze;

===== Meaning =====

pushing a member of a flock, i.e. a  sheep  or  goat

===== Definitions =====

  - pushing
  - sheep
  - goat

===== Usage =====

(lesser, small) cattle, ewe, goat, lamb, sheep. Compare 
